subtitleNullable: Jumia- Customer Ratings of Oraimo Freepods 3 - dataset
descriptionNullable:
This dataset covers the ratings on the Oraimo Freepods 3 over a year after its release. It is a quality product and the data buttresses this point. Check out and - if you can - classify the reviews of the customer base.

The data is available in both csv and xlsx formats

- Customer Name - the name of the customer
- Review Topic - the title and summary of each review
- Review Body - the contents of the reviews
- Rating(of 5) - product score by each customer
- Review date - date of each review
